To Basell. 847. To PETER BARBIRIUS. Deventer MS. 91, f. 17. Basle. LB. App. 284. 31 May 1518.

[This and Ep. 848 are copied by a new hand, E, evidently someone engaged at Basle. For some reason he did not stay long in Erasmus' service, the only other work by him in the MS. being numerations of some of the leaves (see vol. i, pp. 605765. The date is unquestionable]
